data.description: A unique affordable home, first house on a private road. Minutes to Beacon, Metro North train, Rte 84, making commuting a breeze. Loaded with all the essential upgrades, done for you in the last 2 years, new roof, new boiler, oil tank, gutters, flooring, doors and a new 1250 gallon septic tank adding significant value and peace of mind.  Tax records show 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath but with new larger septic it can be used as a 3-4 bedroom plus office, 8 rooms 1584 sq. ft. to revamp anyway you need it. The inclusion of two lots in the sale is yet another bonus, offering extra space, privacy and potential for future expansion. Large Bedrooms, Kitchen, Dining Room, Living Room, Office. Growing family, extended family or mother daughter possibilities. Practical features like a level fenced yard, generator hookup, new stainless-steel appliances, cathedral ceilings, laundry in basement. Situated Fishkill Township within the Beacon School District will add appeal for some potential buyers.
